                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8676" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2178</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1750 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">德美果全产业链布局——助力“红果果”变身致富“金担担”之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Whole Industrial Chain Layout of DeMei Fruit——Paving the Way for the Transformation of &quot;Red Fruit&quot; into a Golden Opportunity for Prosperity </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邱璐，赵乐诗，欧阳其斌，郭华，崔丽，李菁</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北农林科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">甘肃德美地缘现代农业集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">25 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">德美果；企业使命；企业愿景；全产业链；纵向一体化；2024百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Demei apples; Corporate mission; Corporate vision; Whole industrial chain; Vertical integration</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">甘肃德美地缘现代农业集团有限公司是一家集科学育苗、生态种植、冷链储存、终端销售于一体的农业产业化国家重点龙头企业，秉承“德行天下，美洒人间”的企业宗旨，致力于将静宁苹果打造成中国苹果第一品牌，成为有品质的幸福企业。本案例重点分析了该公司凭借特有的“倒着来的产业链”创业思维和“三品三化三支撑”经营理念，整合产业链上中下游各环节资源，完成德美果全产业链布局，助力静宁果农脱贫致富的过程。案例旨在帮助学生理解并掌握有关企业使命、愿景和价值观的理论知识，提高对涉农企业全产业链及纵向一体化战略的认识，培养学生的战略思维能力，增强社会责任感和使命感。同时，为市场同类型涉农企业实施全产业链模式、推动地方特色农业高质量发展、实现共同富裕提供经验借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Gansu Demei Diyuan Modern Agriculture Group Co., Ltd. is a nationally recognized leading enterprise in agricultural industrialization, integrating scientific seedling cultivation, ecological planting, cold chain storage, and end-market sales. Adhering to the corporate philosophy of &quot;Acting according to ethical principles and spreading goodness throughout the world&quot;, the company is committed to establishing Jingning apples as the leading apple brand in China and to becoming a quality-driven, happiness-oriented enterprise. This case study focuses on the company&#39;s unique &quot;reverse industry chain&quot; entrepreneurial approach and its &quot;Three Qualities, Three Transformations, and Three Supports&quot; management philosophy. It analyzes how the company integrated resources across the upstream, midstream, and downstream segments of the industrial chain to establish the whole industrial chain of Demei fruits, thereby aiding fruit farmers in Jingning County in achieving poverty alleviation and prosperity. This case study aims to help students understand and master the theoretical knowledges related to corporate mission, vision, and values. It also seeks to enhance students&#39; awareness of the whole industrial chain and vertical integration strategies in agricultural enterprises, foster strategic thinking abilities, and strengthen their sense of social responsibility and mission. Additionally, it provides valuable insights for similar agricultural enterprises in the market on implementing whole industrial chain models, promoting high-quality development of regional specialty agriculture, and achieving common prosperity.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《产业链管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业愿景、使命和价值观理论；全产业链模式；纵向一体化战略；竞争优势理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
